pageContext.title: AB:16
pageContext.description: On the nose, clove and nutmeg, cafe au lait, subtle dark fruit notes, and hints of candied lemon peel. On the palate, smooth & fruity espresso, milk chocolate, and warm brandy-soaked currants are in the middle of a high-class dance-off against the spicy and peppery Belgian character. The overall impression evokes malt loaf or ginger cake.
pageContext.author: Ali Skinner <AliSkinner>
